  "elements": [
    {
      "id": "0jnkuXQ4ZzsJAMo89zy39",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 20127.398183253426,
      "y": 948.1112321832557,
      "width": 1473.862548828125,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#846358",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 777022723,
      "version": 71,
      "versionNonce": 433334669,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779977367439,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional requirements:\n    - Users should be able to start, pause, stop, and save their runs and rides.\n    - While running or cycling, users should be able to view activity data, including route, distance, and time.\n    - Users should be able to view details about their own completed activities as well as the activities of their friends.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional requirements:\n    - Users should be able to start, pause, stop, and save their runs and rides.\n    - While running or cycling, users should be able to view activity data, including route, distance, and time.\n    - Users should be able to view details about their own completed activities as well as the activities of their friends.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PGTDBy9QGUNhV8mJz_Qpq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 20127.290307442694,
      "y": 1171.0796171970453,
      "width": 662.0316162109375,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#846358",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 456075565,
      "version": 32,
      "versionNonce": 1809558733,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779977366155,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Out of Scope:\n    - Adding or deleting friends (friend management).\n    - Authentication and authorization.\n    - Commenting or liking runs.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Out of Scope:\n    - Adding or deleting friends (friend management).\n    - Authentication and authorization.\n    - Commenting or liking runs.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SeSjeZdTYIw6c_QfDnDQc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 20133.41547712179,
      "y": 1401.7824165488153,
      "width": 1249.779052734375,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#846358",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1165771149,
      "version": 74,
      "versionNonce": 520779373,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779977362331,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Non functional requirements:\n    - system should be highly available (availability >> consistency).\n    - app should function in remote areas without network connectivity.\n    - app should provide the athlete with accurate and up-to-date local statistics during the run/ride.\n    - system should scale to support 10 million concurrent activities.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Non functional requirements:\n    - system should be highly available (availability >> consistency).\n    - app should function in remote areas without network connectivity.\n    - app should provide the athlete with accurate and up-to-date local statistics during the run/ride.\n    - system should scale to support 10 million concurrent activities.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "fuFvQgrNnuc5V-NWsEzvC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 20121.218703414528,
      "y": 1664.1362037176373,
      "width": 709.2955322265625,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#846358",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2090997827,
      "version": 28,
      "versionNonce": 1432273837,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779977365139,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Out of Scope:\n    - compliance with data privacy regulations like GDPR.\n    - advanced security measures",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Out of Scope:\n    - compliance with data privacy regulations like GDPR.\n    - advanced security measures",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "X8nFxiiPy6FZwFX31BkFi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 20136.259103575343,
      "y": 1866.934109978749,
      "width": 165.619873046875,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#846358",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5N",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1231807491,
      "version": 95,
      "versionNonce": 112315661,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779977370456,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core entities:\n    - User\n    - Activity\n    - Route\n    - Friend",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core entities:\n    - User\n    - Activity\n    - Route\n    - Friend",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wR8yDUBembv5J3tgTRcNG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 20129.59441179006,
      "y": 2118.4719114978066,
      "width": 1473.862548828125,
      "height": 1085,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#846358",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 645526275,
      "version": 177,
      "versionNonce": 450838925,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779977371405,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API:\n    - Users should be able to start, pause, stop, and save their runs and rides.\n    POST /api/v1/activities -> Activity\n    Headers: JWT\n    body: {\n        type: \"RUN\" | \"RIDE\"\n    }\n\n    PATCH /api/v1/activities/{activityId} -> Activity\n    Headers: JWT\n    body: {\n        state: \"STARTED\" | \"PAUSED\" | \"COMPLETE\"\n    }\n\n    - While running or cycling, users should be able to view activity data, including route, distance, and time.\n    POST /api/v1/activities/{activityId}/routes -> Activity\n    Headers: JWT\n    body: {\n        location: GPSCoordinate,\n    }\n\n    - Users should be able to view details about their own completed activities as well as the activities of their friends.\n    GET /api/v1/activities?mode={USER|FRIENDS}&page={page}&pageSize={pageSize} -> Partial<Activity>[]\n    Headers: JWT\n\n\n    GET /activities/{activityId} -> Activity\n    Headers: JWT\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API:\n    - Users should be able to start, pause, stop, and save their runs and rides.\n    POST /api/v1/activities -> Activity\n    Headers: JWT\n    body: {\n        type: \"RUN\" | \"RIDE\"\n    }\n\n    PATCH /api/v1/activities/{activityId} -> Activity\n    Headers: JWT\n    body: {\n        state: \"STARTED\" | \"PAUSED\" | \"COMPLETE\"\n    }\n\n    - While running or cycling, users should be able to view activity data, including route, distance, and time.\n    POST /api/v1/activities/{activityId}/routes -> Activity\n    Headers: JWT\n    body: {\n        location: GPSCoordinate,\n    }\n\n    - Users should be able to view details about their own completed activities as well as the activities of their friends.\n    GET /api/v1/activities?mode={USER|FRIENDS}&page={page}&pageSize={pageSize} -> Partial<Activity>[]\n    Headers: JWT\n\n\n    GET /activities/{activityId} -> Activity\n    Headers: JWT\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
