      "updated": 1779981622728,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5. How can we support realtime sharing of activities with friends?\n     ❌ Websocket/SSE - over-engineering\n     ❌ Pub-sub to broadcast - over-engineering\n     ✅ Polling mechanism will be more effective\n            - Updates are predictable\n            - Real-time precision isn't critical",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5. How can we support realtime sharing of activities with friends?\n     ❌ Websocket/SSE - over-engineering\n     ❌ Pub-sub to broadcast - over-engineering\n     ✅ Polling mechanism will be more effective\n            - Updates are predictable\n            - Real-time precision isn't critical",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
