      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779981762054,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "6. How can we expose a leaderboard of top athletes?\n    ❌ Query the DB for all activities and then group them by user and sum the distance\n    ✅ Periodic aggregation\n            - background job would run at regular intervals to update these aggregates based on new activities\n    ✅ ✅ Realtime leaderboard with Redis\n            -  use Redis Sorted Sets to maintain leaderboards\n        ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "6. How can we expose a leaderboard of top athletes?\n    ❌ Query the DB for all activities and then group them by user and sum the distance\n    ✅ Periodic aggregation\n            - background job would run at regular intervals to update these aggregates based on new activities\n    ✅ ✅ Realtime leaderboard with Redis\n            -  use Redis Sorted Sets to maintain leaderboards\n        ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
